name: Mohair Me Crazy Sweater
description:
Cozy gray mohair+wool sweater with flecks of color in the wool. Style it with some knee highs and creepers for a perfect fall look. 

Fits medium.
Fabric: wool + mohair.

name: Vice Tank
description:
Badass mesh tank perfect for layering. Try with an all black look or throw it over some neon. Either way you'll have the boys drooling. 

Fits small.

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week

name: Empire Record Doc's
description:
Doc Marten classic lace up loafer. The 90's are back. 

Size: 7
Made in: China (from when the company moved production over seas.. don't worry they're legit)

name: Bardot Leather Biker Shorts
description:
Ready for you to hop on a motorcycle and cruise the night away. Bridgett would approve.

Waist: 29"
Length: 16" (can be cuffed shorted)

name: Disco T-shirt
description:
This textured t-shirt gives off early 90's vibe to perfection. 

Fits medium to large (but can be knotted in the back for a more fitted look).

name: Melrose Boot
description:
Chunky, grunge boot love. Perfect for short skirts or cuffed jeans.  Now all you need is a man on a motorcycle.

Size: 8
Heel: 2.5"
Label: Two Lips

name: Anna Sui Furriness
description:
The perfect balance of classiness + funky fuzz. 

Size small
Fabric: Mohair/Wool/Nylon

name: Salem Robe
description:
This witchy robe has black fur detailing along the sleeves and lapels making it extremely unique.

Fits large to extra large (But we think it looks pretty rad on Kate's smaller frame).

Length: 40"

name: Madeline Tartan Skirt
description:
Perfect plaid skirt for channeling your inner Courtney Love. So rad. 

Fits medium.
Waist: 30"
Length: 19.5"

name: Oxlood Leather Pants
description:
These buttery leather pants are to DIE for. 

Waist: 26"
Inseam: 32" (27" with a cuff)
Length from waist to inseam: 12.5"
Damage: scratches on leather at the bottom of the leg, but is covered by the cuff. 

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week

name: Gauzy Leopard Blouse
description:
Purrfect sheer leopard blouse in a gorgeous gauzy silk. 

Fits large to extra large, but hangs beautifully on everyone. 
Fabric: 100% silk.

name: Escada Dolphin Blouse
description:
Everyone can appreciate some friendly dolphins jumping across their chest, especially if it's Escada. 

Size small
Fabric: 100% silk

name: Courtney Ankle Boot
description:
The most amazing black grunge-esque boot you could ask for. 

Size: 10 (9 fits fine)
Heel: 4"
Label: Candies
 
Zippers on inside.

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week

name: Dooney & Bourke Purse
description: Cream and tan leather front flap purse. Very Alexa Chung.

name: Animal Instincts Maxi
description:
A girl's wardrobe isn't complete without a little leopard print in her life. Get some. Rawrrrr.

Size medium
Waist: 29" elastic.
Length: 36.5" 

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week

name: Austin Tank
description:
Toughen up in this textured black tank. 

Size large (Knot the front or back for a more fitted look)

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week

name: Shanghai Blouse
description:
Sheer, bold oriental print on a sheer flowy fabric. Yum. 

Fits large to extra large.

name: Olive Blouse
description:
Sheer, textured blouse in a gorgeous velvet material. 

Fits large (again, looks rad oversized)

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week

name: Sporty Spice Jacket
description:
Don't come near this jacket if you're afraid of nostalgic feelings taking over every time you wear it. We think it's the perfect combination of neon and textured sport wear. Tell me what you want what you really really want. 

Size medium to large, but we think any size can pull it off.

name: Juliette Beaded Robe
description:
This stunning, hand sewn beaded robe is hard to part with, but we know someone will love it just as much as we do. 

Size medium
Length: 51.5"

Damage: small stain on back of arm

name: Christian Dior Garden Blouse
description:
Add a bright splash of color to your wardrobe with this floral Christian Dior piece. Looks amazing worn loose and oversized or worn knotted in the front. 

Fits a large to extra large.

name: Leather Maxi
description:
Glorious is the only way to describe this maxi skirt. Buttery, soft leather with an amazing Angelina slit up the leg. 

Waist: 28.5"
Length: 40"
Waist to top of slit: 16"

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week

name: Marla Boot
description:
The leather boot that Blossom's badass cousin would have been wearing. 

Size: 7.5
Heel: 2.5"
Label: Steve Madden
Made in: Brazil

name: Daria Loafer
description:
Leather cut-out Doc Marten flats. 

Size: 8 
Made in: England
Label: Doc Marten's

name: The Perfect Silk Tank
description:
The essential cream silk tank, need we say more?

Fits large to extra large, but drapes beautifully off anyone. (Knot it in the front or back for a more fitted look)
Fabric: 100 % Silk

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week

name: Metallic Bowie Robe
description:
We love how this cobalt blue robe drapes perfectly off anybody. Dance the night away in this metallic gem... David approves (we're on a first name basis, duh).  

Fits large (anysize)
Length 29"

name: Leather Coach Purse
description: The classic vintage Coach purse. Thick, gorgeous leather that'll last forever. A definite must-have.

name: Silk Shanghai Kimono
description:
Whether you are new to kimonos or a seasoned wearer, this is the easiest piece to add to your collection. It's perfect. 

Size: One size fits most
Length: 52"
Fabric: Silk

name: Dolce & Gabbana Mesh Skirt
description:
The raddest knee length skirt you'll ever want. Perfect condition in all it's mesh/sheer glory. We'd wear it with a wild one piece underneath. 

Fits medium.
Waist: 30" (hangs at your hips)
Length: 24"
Label: Dolce & Gabbana Mare (their high end resort collection).

name: English Country Jacket
description:
This plaid coat will make you feel like you should be running around Notting Hill with Hugh Grant. Oversized in the best way possible and the fringe detail around the bottom adds the perfect festival vibe. 

Fits extra large (but looks great on a size medium).
Fabric: wool

name: Gisele Polka-Dot Blouse
description:
Stunning silk blouse to add the perfect pop of color to your outfit. It also doesn't hurt that polka-dots were seen all over the runway for this season.

Fabric: 100% Silk
Fits large (but we think any size can pull it off)

name: Market Blouse
description:
Creamy silkiness with the most mom-esque print you could imagine. 
In love. 

Fits a medium. 
Fabric: 100% silk perfection.

name: Marc Jacobs Tiger Tee
description:
Meoow.. this t-shirt looks so incredible styled up in any way. 

Fits medium.
The Marc Jacobs label is ripped up a bit, but either way, it doesn't affect how rad this looks on!

name: Red Silk Bomber
description:
Bold red + silk + diamond cross stitching, you can't ask for anything better!

Fits small to medium.
Fabric: silk with light lining to keep you warm

name: Metallic Turtle-neck
description:
Turtle-necks can be a scary thing. Terrifying for some, actually. But we dare you to not like this one. All that metallic, body-con perfection. Meoowww.  

Fits small to medium.

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week

name: Japanese Dragon Kimono
description:
Stunning silk kimono. 

One size fits most.
Length: 59"

Damage: Discoloring on the silk in places.

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week (closed the show)

name: Sabrina Sheer Long-sleeve
description:
Sheer long sleeve, perfect for creating an architectural look. 

Fits medium to large.
Fabric is very delicate.

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week

name: Christian Dior Leather Belt
description: Wear around our leather biker shorts with a silk white tank in a knot for the perfect edgy look.

name: Red Wing Combat
description:
Steel toe Red Wing boots. The perfect combat that'll have all the boys drooling. 

Size: 6 - 6.5 (labelled at size 4 Mens or 24cm)
Made in: USA
Mint condition.

name: Wednesday Mesh Tank
description:
This heavy mesh tank is a necessity in your wardrobe. Pair with anything from a leather skirt to a beautiful cascading robe, this piece is all about versatility. 

Fits medium-large

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week

name: Glastonbury Tartan Skirt
description:
Your inner school girl is rejoicing about this little number. Adorable 90's esque tartan skirt so you can bring all the boys to the yard. 

The top of the skirt fits right at your natural waist. 

Fabric: wool 
Waist: 25"
Length: 21"

name: Drew Silk Tank
description:
Nazy blue brushed silk tank with flower details on the straps. Slinky, sexy and SO good. Cher Horowitz would approve. 

*Featured in our Fall '13 runway show at Eco Fashion Week
